    {
      "chinese": "[---]依居住地區劃分為五個亞群：（一）南勢阿美：花蓮市、新城鄉、吉安鄉、壽豐鄉。（二）秀姑巒阿美：鳳林鎮、光復鄉、瑞穗鄉、玉里鎮、富里鄉。（三）海岸阿美：豐濱鄉、長濱鄉、成功鎮，東河鄉。（四）馬蘭阿美：成功鎮以南、東河鄉、馬蘭平原一帶等。（五）恆春阿美：鹿野鄉、關山鎮、池上鄉、屏東縣滿州鄉一部份。",
      "ab": "Ano pakaynien i aro’ lima ko kasa’etal no Pangcah. Sakacecay, ’Amisay a Pangcah, o Nafakowan, o Singcen, o Yosino, o Rinahem. [===]Sakatosa, Siwkolang a Pangcah, o Cingalo’an, o Fata’an, o Kohkoh, o Poseko, o Kongpo. Sakatolo, sawaliyay a Pangcah, o Fakong, o Kakacawan, o Madawdaw. Sakasepat, Falangaw a Pangcah, satimolay no Madawdaw, o Fafokod, o dafdaf no Falangaw. Sakalima, Palidaw a Pangcah, o Paliyapay, o Lilong, o Fanaw, o Pingtong no Palidaw.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2025/03/25/a42e41170e04a99e595867ae6723d55b.mp3",
